---
import { TextSection } from '@components/odyssey-theme';
import Layout from '../../layouts/Page.astro';

const seo = {
  title: `Privacy Policy | SatCom & Computers, LLC`,
  description: `Privacy policy outlining how SatCom & Computers, LLC collects, uses, and protects your information, including SMS compliance with 10DLC.`,
};
---

<Layout seo={seo}>
  <TextSection narrow>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="mb-6">Effective Date: May 6, 2025</p>

    <p class="mb-4">SatCom & Computers, LLC ("SatCom," "we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or engage with our IT, telecom, or support services.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">We may collect personal and technical information such as your name, phone number, email address, business name, device data, and communications including SMS sent via 10DLC systems. Phone numbers may be collected for the purpose of sending service-related SMS communications with your consent.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">We use your information to provide services, respond to support requests, send SMS and email communications, and comply with legal obligations.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">3. SMS Communications & Consent</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">By providing your phone number, you consent to receive SMS messages from SatCom & Computers, LLC related to services, support, scheduling, or billing. Message frequency may vary. Message and data rates may apply. You can opt out at any time by replying STOP or request help by replying HELP.</p>

    <p class="mb-4">We will not sell, share, or rent your SMS opt-in information to any third party for any reason other than to deliver the specific services associated with your request or campaign. However, we may share your personal data, including your SMS opt-in status, with third parties that assist in providing messaging services, such as platform providers, carriers, or technology partners involved in delivering the text messages. All the above categories exclude text messaging originator opt-in data and consent; this information will not be shared with third parties for marketing or promotional purposes.</p>

    <p class="mb-4">For more information on SMS usage, refer to our <a href="/company/terms-of-service">Terms of Service</a>.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">4. Sharing Your Information</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">We only share your data with trusted service providers or as required by law. We do not sell your personal information to third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">5. Cookies and Analytics</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">Our site may use cookies and third-party tools for analytics. You may manage cookies in your browser settings.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">6. Data Security</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">We use reasonable safeguards, including encryption and access controls, to protect your data from unauthorized access.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">7. Your Rights</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">You may access, update, or request deletion of your information. To exercise rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@1satcom.com">support@1satcom.com</a>.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">8. Policy Updates</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">We may update this policy periodically. Updates will be posted with the revised effective date.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">9. Contact Us</h3>
    <p>SatCom & Computers, LLC<br />250 S. Capitol St.<br />Many, LA  71449<br /><a href="tel:318-256-1213">318-256-1213</a><br /><a href="mailto:sales@1satcom.com">sales@1satcom.com</a></p>
  </TextSection>
</Layout>